text: Murray Zinzan Valentine Brooke (born 14 February, 1965 in Waiuku, New Zealand) is a New Zealand rugby player who played 58 tests/100 games for New Zealand and Auckland in rugby. He is the older brother of Robin Brooke and is distantly related to Gerard Beale, Zin Harris and Chris Harris. ==Other websites== * Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand rugby union players
